Package: scCATCH
Type: Package
Title: Single Cell Cluster-Based Annotation Toolkit for Cellular Heterogeneity
Version: 3.0
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Author: Xin Shao
Maintainer: Xin Shao<xin_shao@zju.edu.cn>
Description: This package is an automatic cluster-based annotation pipeline 
    based on evidence-based score by matching the marker genes with known cell 
    markers in tissue-specific cell taxonomy reference database.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
